729
00:48:13,036 --> 00:48:14,996
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau siapa, Bu?</font>

730
00:48:15,867 --> 00:48:16,983
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku?</font>

731
00:48:18,255 --> 00:48:19,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan itu yang penting.</font>

732
00:48:19,940 --> 00:48:22,396
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih atas perhatianmu.</font>

733
00:48:22,396 --> 00:48:24,251
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, aku akan mengurus anakku.</font>

734
00:48:24,251 --> 00:48:27,217
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, tapi mengapa Anda membuang
