754
00:49:35,286 --> 00:49:37,235
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayahnya Jin Young?</font>

755
00:49:37,235 --> 00:49:38,762
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

756
00:49:38,762 --> 00:49:41,871
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia meninggal awal tahun ini.</font>

757
00:49:41,871 --> 00:49:46,005
<font color=#FFFF00>Seperti Sung Joon, ayahnya juga mengatakan kalau dia
